        <h2>About <span>SIPOP</span></h2>
        <p>The Scientific Integrity and Publication Oversight Program ensures rigorous, transparent, and ethical research practices in biomedical sciences. Our mission is to elevate research standards by providing thorough review and guidance, minimizing bias, and fostering credibility in scientific publications.</p>
